{"tid":2279020,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【文件泄密】歐盟未來似乎有意 郁 點對點加密通訊軟件 ！！！","createTime":"2020-11-09T13:21:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T15:05:18.000Z","uid":138409,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bc758dfff2881295d37a5ae3e2c44a2cbbf670a4","tid":2279020,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T13:21:44.000Z","msg":"文件：<a href=\"https://files.orf.at/vietnam2/files/fm4/202045/783284_fh_st12143-re01en20_783284.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffiles.orf.at%2Fvietnam2%2Ffiles%2Ffm4%2F202045%2F783284_fh_st12143-re01en20_783284.pdf&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y%2BNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=9afcde62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://files.orf.at/vietnam2/files/fm4/202045/783284_fh_st12143-re01en20_783284.pdf</a><br />\n較早嘅版本：<a href=\"https://www.statewatch.org/media/1352/eu-council-security-despite-encryption-10728-20.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statewatch.org%2Fmedia%2F1352%2Feu-council-security-despite-encryption-10728-20.pdf&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y%2BNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=430263d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.statewatch.org/media/1352/eu-council-security-despite-encryption-10728-20.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n新聞報道：<br />\n（英文）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.itpro.co.uk/security/357699/leaked-memo-suggests-eu-ban-on-end-to-end-encryption-imminent\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.itpro.co.uk%2Fsecurity%2F357699%2Fleaked-memo-suggests-eu-ban-on-end-to-end-encryption-imminent&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y%2BNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=5ddfa262\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.itpro.co.uk/security/357699/leaked-memo-suggests-eu-ban-on-end-to-end-encryption-imminent</a><br />\n<br />\n（德文，詳細脈絡分析，以下會重點翻譯）<br />\n<a href=\"https://fm4.orf.at/stories/3008930/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffm4.orf.at%2Fstories%2F3008930%2F&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y%2BNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=82cc24db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fm4.orf.at/stories/3008930/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">重點</span></span><br />\n- 如果有人唔知乜嘢係點對點加密（E2E）通訊軟件，簡單啲講，類似whatsapp/signal<br />\n<blockquote>End-to-end encryption is intended to prevent data being read or secretly modified, other than by the true sender and recipient(s). The messages are encrypted by the sender <span class=\"gold\">but the third party does not have a means to decrypt them, and stores them encrypted.</span> The recipients retrieve the encrypted data and decrypts it themselves.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n- 篇決議文望落好空泛，<span class=\"gold\">無明確針對 E2E加密</span>；但係個上文下理就喺將E2EE frame做犯罪份子會用嘅工具<br />\n而且 魔鬼在細節中<br />\n<img src=\"https://tubestatic.orf.at/static/images/site/tube/20201145/ohne-titel-2.5944858.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftubestatic.orf.at%2Fstatic%2Fimages%2Fsite%2Ftube%2F20201145%2Fohne-titel-2.5944858.jpg&h=49cd2e9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oDUGz1z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoDUGz1z.png&h=314411cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n問題乜嘢係 「合資格部門」（&ldquo;competent authority&rdquo;）呢？<br />\n<br />\n字眼上可以同五眼聯盟十月出嘅statement做對比，好類似<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.justice.gov/opa/pr/international-statement-end-end-encryption-and-public-safety\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fopa%2Fpr%2Finternational-statement-end-end-encryption-and-public-safety&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y%2BNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=47577b27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.justice.gov/opa/pr/international-statement-end-end-encryption-and-public-safety</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://tubestatic.orf.at/static/images/site/tube/20201145/ohne-titel-1.5944852.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftubestatic.orf.at%2Fstatic%2Fimages%2Fsite%2Ftube%2F20201145%2Fohne-titel-1.5944852.jpg&h=f1c586a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n留意五眼聯盟就開門見山針對E2EE嘅<br />\n<blockquote>In July 2019, the governments of the United Kingdom, United States, Australia, New Zealand and Canada issued a communique, concluding that: &ldquo;tech companies should <span class=\"gold\">include mechanisms in the design of their encrypted products and services whereby governments, acting with appropriate legal authority, can gain access to data in a readable and usable format.</span> Those companies should also embed the safety of their users in their system designs, enabling them to take action against illegal content.&rdquo;</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n具體點 對付E2EE<br />\n份決議文未見明確提議<br />\n但係早前歐盟做過研究，講點樣喺E2E 通訊度偵測child porn<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.politico.eu/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/SKM_C45820090717470-1_new.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.eu%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2FSKM_C45820090717470-1_new.pdf&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y%2BNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=7352e273\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.politico.eu/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/SKM_C45820090717470-1_new.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n其中係「現成方法」（baseline solution）嗰度<br />\n有提到英國政府通信總部（GCHQ） 提出嘅「例外存取」（&ldquo;exceptional access&rdquo;）呢嗰方案<br />\n<img src=\"https://tubestatic.orf.at/static/images/site/tube/20200939/eu_ministerrat_diskussionspapier_ea.5941753.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftubestatic.orf.at%2Fstatic%2Fimages%2Fsite%2Ftube%2F20200939%2Feu_ministerrat_diskussionspapier_ea.5941753.jpg&h=8f63e381&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"xx-large\">簡單啲講，類似裝後門畀情報機構𥄫下你噉</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://fm4.orf.at/stories/2952757/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffm4.orf.at%2Fstories%2F2952757%2F&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y%2BNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=60ad7bc2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fm4.orf.at/stories/2952757/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://tubestatic.orf.at/static/images/site/tube/20181250/gchq_proposal.5832127.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftubestatic.orf.at%2Fstatic%2Fimages%2Fsite%2Ftube%2F20181250%2Fgchq_proposal.5832127.jpg&h=02e0f3f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">邊個推動</span></span><br />\n- 留意最初<span class=\"gold\">唔係歐盟自己推先</span>，事實上2017年嘅時候，歐州議會打算強制要求通信服務提供者（通訊軟件之類）要用E2EE；但係當時英國反對<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.itpro.co.uk/data-protection/28883/eu-proposes-mandatory-end-to-end-encryption-for-all-citizens\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.itpro.co.uk%2Fdata-protection%2F28883%2Feu-proposes-mandatory-end-to-end-encryption-for-all-citizens&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y%2BNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=a14eb7a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.itpro.co.uk/data-protection/28883/eu-proposes-mandatory-end-to-end-encryption-for-all-citizens</a><br />\n<br />\n- 推動力來自歐洲刑警組織、FBI、五眼聯盟之類<br />\n- 而家法國推行得幾落力，契機係最近嘅法國恐襲<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">進度</span></span><br />\n- 份決議案，唔單止寫好曬，睇嚟已經係歐盟理事會（由來自28個歐盟成員國各國政府部長所組成的理事會）投票初步通過埋<br />\n- 所謂理事會決議案（council resolution），即係 <span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">無。約。束。力</span></span>嘅；但係就表達成員國立場，<span class=\"gold\">反映未來政策嘅方向</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.consilium.europa.eu/en/council-eu/conclusions-resolutions/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.consilium.europa.eu%2Fen%2Fcouncil-eu%2Fconclusions-resolutions%2F&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y%2BNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=154ee337\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.consilium.europa.eu/en/council-eu/conclusions-resolutions/</a><br />\nCouncil resolutions usually set out future work foreseen in a specific policy area. They have no legal effect but they can invite the Commission to make a proposal or take further action."},{"pid":"0db255434b4cb64e2bab34179de3ed8c333f57b9","tid":2279020,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T13:22:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c39e09743d792fc097893e65cce4206e9086302e","tid":2279020,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T13:22:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2e0c29916823ca4e9d16275e757b46d7f5474995","tid":2279020,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T13:23:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bca3562ec1416a9b421e10fc6671d79cdb30b4c8","tid":2279020,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T13:25:44.000Z","msg":"On9<br />\n監控佢老母呀"},{"pid":"c156e433286f2a4764a80649e5fc7e7a71252af0","tid":2279020,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T13:28:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e3c0b478b75e88ec4ad3ba59fc58eb07481e8f92","tid":2279020,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T13:29:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3cfa24bf88888ed92efc595b0065f4a2ae473299","tid":2279020,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T13:31:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"85e685b5924bbcf9a49e882f16c8d278c68635c1","tid":2279020,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T13:32:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c7370f57a3c286c7d46e7b98e7ff4174e35f4d0f","tid":2279020,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T13:33:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c18d067bdf217a628396760d4d09bc02ebdaeb1a","tid":2279020,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85e685b5924bbcf9a49e882f16c8d278c68635c1","tid":2279020,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T13:32:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T13:33:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a453c79a5fcd1604e7ccb1cfb18376b1f216a62","tid":2279020,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislik